{"tid":847790,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"請問而家邊度仲有好食嘅牛油雞翼？","createTime":"2018-10-04T12:07:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-22T16:43:01.000Z","uid":190666,"like":21,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"80f36a73c300e217f0a49a629c54b72bb7992f64","tid":847790,"uid":190666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T12:07:56.000Z","msg":"細個啊爸啊媽成日帶我去銅鑼灣食牛油雞翼<br />\n由當初嘅清亭燕萍到後來嘅越南蔡<br />\n到越南蔡都執埋之後<br />\n食過好多間都搵唔返當初嘅味道<br />\n有無同道中人知而家邊度仲有得食到類似嘅牛油雞翼？<br />\n要係充滿牛油香 唔係用現成炸蒜粒<br />\n而係用牛油炸蒜蓉而D蒜仲係濕濕地嘅<br />\n<br />\n而家諗起都流哂口水<br />\n真係好多年無食過啦<br />\n好掛住啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/04/200216_d8c89d6ce26425daa186b5f7638448d8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F04%2F200216_d8c89d6ce26425daa186b5f7638448d8.jpg&h=0a61453f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6f1171b1ba950f8581ae61513f850c64ca6832fa","tid":847790,"uid":82420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T12:10:32.000Z","msg":"大叻"},{"pid":"6ec3c296f3980ca036d2cefab0235185874421a8","tid":847790,"uid":190666,"like":0,"dislike":14,"score":-14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T12:32:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/04/202952_64bfe9e37657937b36783000497e648b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F04%2F202952_64bfe9e37657937b36783000497e648b.jpg&h=54eccea6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nOpenrice睇到唔係嗰回事<br />\n重點係嗰d牛油蒜蓉 撈飯一流<br />\n呢張圖見唔到有嗰D牛油蒜蓉粒"},{"pid":"a5896cbc12c2016480433f8e7d731e4e4cb95aca","tid":847790,"uid":1249,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T12:33:27.000Z","msg":"自己整啦，好簡單"},{"pid":"7f7421728ab1e306e5c21ee46837f8baaf736804","tid":847790,"uid":56798,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"reply